{"tid":2224602,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪蠢人先會做善良嘅人？","createTime":"2020-09-30T15:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T12:58:50.000Z","uid":229709,"like":102,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"e52467982cca0697d9aa2b0e0ddf80d95fec5536","tid":2224602,"uid":229709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:32:57.000Z","msg":"大家有無識得一啲人係 各方面都真係好outstanding, 但份人都依然好善良？ <br />\n(係打從心底嗰種善良，唔係為呃like/ 唔係形象工程/唔係捐少少錢都要po Ig story 嗰種)<br />\n<br />\n點解咁問係因為我成日都覺得真係好醒目好叻嘅人，會真係善良嘅比例好似小啲？<br />\n太醒目令佢喺呢個社會有太多野可以參與，比較容易名成利就，就唔會咁有同理心同善良<br />\n<br />\n點睇？ 交流交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1a363421db976edb64f87e8c1b3d69fa5ce33e","tid":2224602,"uid":229709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:34:41.000Z","msg":"自推3連"},{"pid":"ec41a8ced57339a9c20f527c14b4e8e453870219","tid":2224602,"uid":229709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:34:59.000Z","msg":"自推3連<br />\n 2/3"},{"pid":"41d084a246dfa8f55d67deadc6d2a1fc1dc90223","tid":2224602,"uid":229709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:35:12.000Z","msg":"自推3連 <br />\n3/3"},{"pid":"30372642603e538307b265c2e9b53815ee6aade9","tid":2224602,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:35:21.000Z","msg":"蕭生點睇都唔似蠢掛"},{"pid":"a07db38da2ebb267e589b1c2a61678e5e77c2b93","tid":2224602,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:35:50.000Z","msg":"蕭生咪善良 日日分享知識傳教"},{"pid":"c7970fe8bd8dd7eba34893eed2ff72366aabe519","tid":2224602,"uid":228143,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:38:53.000Z","msg":"所以蕭生咪上左神台 <br />\n<br />\n睇咁多書咁老仲貼地過後生<br />\n<br />\n日日睇韓劇 去景點 又出片<br />\n<br />\n佢都話冇咩遺憾 <br />\n<br />\n正宗行得太快等死<br />\n<br />\n咩hku結婚仔女成材<br />\n<br />\n編劇 網台都違成晒<br />\n<br />\n幾多人追求一樣成世都搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":